node.text:
People are offended by everything because they do not guard their heart like Jesus has told us. Your emotions are fleeting and can mislead you. Living your life based on feelings cannot bring stability or peace. The world says “follow your heart” but God says “Follow Me.” 

“Guard your heart above all else, for it determines the course of your life.”
‭‭- Proverbs‬ ‭4:23‬ ‭

“For God hath not given us the spirit of fear; but of power, and of love, and of a sound mind.”
‭‭- 2 Timothy‬ ‭1:7‬ ‭

New YouTube video is on my channel all about how “Wokeness” is trying to ruin America.

node.title: A generation led by “feelings” and rejection for truth.

node.text:
Share this post!!! This whistleblower is one of many to step forward. Without them, I wouldn’t have understood just how far Sephora was willing to go to defame me and ruin my career. This fight is not just about me but about everyone’s individual liberties in this Nation. When a company can spread defamatory lies about your character, which results in you losing your job, we are no longer living in a free country. Freedom of Speech means even the voices you disagree with. 

If you’ve encountered discrimination with @sephora and want to share your story, please e-mail AmandaEnsingPR@gmail.com
📩 All identifying information is kept anonymous. #boycottsephora

node.text:
Biden gets two Beauty influencers, @mannymua733 @jackieaina, who took part in bullying/encouraging the beauty industry to cancel me for my conservative views and faith, to push the 💉. They said everyone has to get the shot to “do their part” and to get it if you “care about other peoples health.” Biden also said many black communities can’t get access to get it because they don’t have cars and live 500 miles away from pharmacies, that they don’t have access to health resources. Jackie, a social media justice warrior against racism, smiled and thanked Biden as he insinuated black communities are poor or less than white people. 

These influencers called me racist, ugly, asked for brands to stop sponsoring me, mocked my Christian views, and more. They follow and support IG accounts who’s sole purpose is to “cancel” and destroy people’s careers. It’s hypocrisy that Beauty brands such as Sephora continue to sponsor them, despite their lies and defamatory attempts against myself and other conservatives. Despite their lack of respect, acceptance, or inclusion of people who aren’t liberal. Liberal influencers are able to speak their minds and bully others who disagree, while conservatives are de-platformed, lose their jobs, or are cancelled. These “influencers” are just being used to push a narrative. Their “inclusivity” and “equality” ends where your differing political views begin. 
Siri, define pandering.

node.text: The fact that the media is making her look like a hero in this situation is all you need to know. They never cared about any of her past tweets, so what makes you think they care now? Hollywood won’t “cancel” one of their own, nor will brands stop sponsoring her, because they’re all at the same dinners and in the same clubs. Her behavior is VILE. Stop giving your time and money to these people. Without an audience, there is no Hollywood. @target , are you going to keep Chrissy Teigen’s products in your stores? You’ve removed others for much less. Time to put action to the values you claim to have.

node.title: Chrissy Teigen tells a teenager to end her life.

node.text: Freedom doesn’t end where media-induced fear begins. Freedom does not infringe on another persons liberty to reject things that will harm them and seek what is pure and honorable.

node.text:
Comment Amen if you are trusting God with your future 🙋🏻‍♀️ Sometimes, God let’s things die so revival can come, so HE can revive it. Do you believe that Jesus will open doors that no man can shut and shut doors that no man can open? That God makes a way when there is no way? Are you expectant for a flood of fresh water in the dry areas of your life? Don’t underestimate the power of prayer and obedience. Even though many are asleep to the season we are in, breakthrough is coming. 🌊🙏🏽

“but they that wait upon the LORD shall renew their strength; they shall mount up with wings as eagles; they shall run, and not be weary; and they shall walk, and not faint." - ‭‭Isaiah‬ ‭40:31‬ ‭

(outfit linked on my stories & LIKEtoKNOW.it)

node.text: Lockdowns are for the rich and mental health matters. 🌱 @charliekirk1776 made a powerful video with some of these stats. I don’t know about y’all but I don’t live in fear, I live free 🇺🇸 We need each other now more than ever. 🤝 Remember, the same people pushing lockdowns and for your business to close, never missed a paycheck.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Amanda Ensing on August 01, 2021. May be an image of flower and indoor.

node.text:
Are you living free or in fear? “Do NOT Fear!” Jesus commands us throughout the Bible (Isaiah 35:4). The Bible leaves no room for fear or doubt. You cannot have faith and fear at the same time. You cannot believe Gods truth and mans truth at the same time. Knowing that fear does not come from God, shows us that it comes from other places. In unprecedented times, remember this simple truth, for it will embolden you. Now is the time to stand, speak, and preserve freedom, to protect the glory of God. Stop worrying about what people will think, what people will say. Start worrying about what Jesus thinks. Speaking truth is the greatest act of love for thy neighbor. If not now, then when? The tide is turning my friends, and God wins 🕊

“Why are the nations so angry? Why do they waste their time with futile plans? The kings of the earth prepare for battle; the rulers plot together against the Lord and against his anointed one. “Let us break their chains,” they cry, “and free ourselves from slavery to God.” But the one who rules in heaven laughs. The Lord scoffs at them.” - Psalms‬ ‭2:1-4‬ ‭

(Outfit is linked on my LIKEtoKNOW.it and stories)

node.text: Truth will sound like hate to those who hate the truth. Put on the full armour of God 🙏🏽

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Amanda Ensing on July 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text:
The world wants strong, outspoken women, until they’re strong & outspoken. Don’t let the world muzzle your voice. God has chosen you out of the world and you were set apart. Be bold and brave like Esther, use your voice to inspire like Deborah, be faithful like Mary, be loyal like Ruth. 

“And blessed is she that believed: for there shall be a performance of those things which were told her from the Lord.”
‭‭- Luke‬ ‭1:45‬ ‭

Tag a strong woman in your life 💛
